[Action Mission Codes\Walk Thru Walls]
author=Code Master
description=With this code, Press L1+Select to Activate it & L2+Select to De-activate it. To avoid falling thru the floor, we had to disable jumping with this code, so if you need to jump you will need to De-activate this code first. You will also have Infinite Health to avoid dying soon as you re-enter from the other side of a wall in a location where you would normally be 'falling'.
